{
  "stem": "24231.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But George Brady was involved mostly in manual work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wasn't the type of writing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the only copy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't-- I haven't seen it myself since the time I-- I brought it to-- to that orphanage.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe next year, I will try to go to Theresienstadt and see it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I guess, I said [INAUDIBLE] [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at-- at the beginning, I was very, very upset when I seen people being carried, dead people being carried on these little wagons into the morgues.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and then on top of it, bringing even bodies with 50 dead people on a flatbed to the crematorium or even to be buried.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After a while, you, I guess, the human being becomes used to anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I just became just, like, oblivious to anything that was happening around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is a story behind it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was put into a-- into a transport.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what happened is my father told me, look, I will try to talk to the SS man, Rahm, and tell him that my son is in the-- in the transport and if he could take you out.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If he-- and what-- what happened is there were some reviews of people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went in front of Rahm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came in front of him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, I am the son of the blacksmith, Taussig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I lied to him, I work in the blacksmith's also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and he-- because my father was a real good blacksmith and he was hoofing his horses, and out of mercy, I think, he took me out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So my father was the really one who saved me from going to-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Otherwise, I would have been in the camp, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
